cast.overview: Marcus and Mike are forced to confront new threats, career changes, and midlife crises as they join the newly created elite team AMMO of the Miami police department to take down the ruthless Armando Armas, the vicious leader of a Miami drug cartel.
cast.title: Bad Boys for Life

details.biography: Nick Rivera Caminero, popularly known in the music world as Nicky Jam, is an American urban music singer and songwriter. He was born on March 17, 1981 in Boston, Massachusetts; he is of Puerto Rican descent on his father's side and Dominican descent on his mother's side.
details.name: Nicky Jam
